description: Comprehensive TypeScript quality review of White Cross Healthcare Platform frontend

workstreams.description: Review type definitions, identify 'any' usage, verify interfaces
Compare types across pages, check for duplication and shared types
Review try-catch blocks, error types, and error handling patterns
Analyze API response handling, null checks, and validation
Check for unused imports, documentation, magic numbers, naming
Generate comprehensive quality report with recommendations

decisions.decision: Found extensive 'any' type usage in error handlers - recommend specific error types
Identified inconsistent API response handling across pages - recommend standardization
Found good type organization but some duplication - recommend consolidation
